        <p class="privacy-p">In general, the information collected by our server includes the Internet Protocol (IP) addresses of the visitor’s device which connects it to the internet. Our web servers collect the domain names, not the e-mail addresses, of visitors. The visitor may knowingly choose to disclose certain Personal Information that is collected on an individual basis. The information collected from you may include your name, address, telephone and/or e-mail address, etc. We do not knowingly collect personal information from minors.</p>
