    </div>
    <div class="container p-3">
        <h2 class="privacy-h2">Registration Information :</h2>
        <p class="privacy-p">You will provide us information about yourself that will enable us to verify whether you are entitled to access and use certain information, materials and services available on our Website. This information may also be used to enable us to enhance your website visit, to assist you with technical support services, or to follow up with you after your visit, or to otherwise support your relationship with GKTC. It is completely optional for you to share your Personal Information. However, you may not be able to access some features and services of our website, if you wish to not to share the required Personal Information. For Log-on to certain areas of the Website, where you may be prompted to provide us with your Log in Name and set Password as a condition to gaining access to certain information, materials or services.
        </p>
