            <li>Register or sign-up to use a service.</li>
            <li>Subscribe to a newsletter or desire to be added to our mailing lists for other products and services.</li>
            <li>Use customized services.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="privacy-p">In each of the instances above, we typically ask for your name, e-mail address, phone number, address, Log in Name and Password, as well as, other similar personal information that is needed to register or subscribe you to services. On occasion, we may ask for additional information to enable us to provide you with access to and use of certain special features, information and services.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="container p-3">
        <h2 class="privacy-h2">Use Of Collected Information :</h2>
        <p class="privacy-p">Domain name information that we collect is not used to personally identify you and instead is aggregated to measure the number of visits, average time spent on the site, pages viewed, etc. We use this information to measure the use of our website and to improve its content. To develop our services and to improve and modify the website.</p>
