        <p class="privacy-p">We may use business contact information (e.g., name, address, email, and phone number), job title, banking information etc. of our vendors/suppliers specifically for the purpose of fulfilling our contractual obligations, including paying charges/fees for receiving goods and services etc. from the vendors/suppliers and/ or to ensure compliance with applicable legal requirements.</p>
        <p class="privacy-p">GKTC uses your Personal Information for specific purposes only. The Personal Information you provide to us when using the website or availing our services will be kept confidential and used to support your relationship with GKTC, to notify you about our services, update about any new services, to update you about the status of your existing services, if any etc. Agents or vendors of GKTC who are given access to your Personal Information will be required to keep the information confidential and not to use it for any other purpose other than to carry out the services they are performing for GKTC.</p>
        <p class="privacy-p">We will keep your data for as long as necessary to fulfill our purposes, to execute our contracts and to comply with any legal obligation. The data that we collect based on your consent will be kept until you withdraw your consent.</p>
        <p class="privacy-p">Subject to applicable law, you can request for deletion or correction of your data shared with GKTC.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="container p-3">
